9
00:01:30,501 --> 00:01:31,846
In fact, I would say it's the same.

10
00:01:32,707 --> 00:01:36,977
But the tradition is taken from the Tibetan tradition of the Medicine Buddha.

11
00:01:37,478 --> 00:01:42,250
The practice is taken from the Tibetan tradition of the Medicine Buddha.

12
00:01:42,311 --> 00:01:44,996
And then we can share it.

13
00:01:45,635 --> 00:01:57,045
If you've got people in the house, you can share it with them, whether they know that or not, or your neighbors, and then we can share it to all beings in all directions.

14
00:02:03,709 --> 00:02:15,539
Okay, so let's get into a nice contemplative posture to make sure that your body is the expression of the enlightened mind of the awakened one.

15
00:02:16,819 --> 00:02:19,383
Just that energy coming up the spine.

16
00:02:24,551 --> 00:02:34,947
Spending a moment just relaxing.

17
