For both this exercise and Meta, it's good to feel comfortable, so feel free to move your position.

18
00:03:27,390 --> 00:03:34,278
So our first contemplations are to undermine the sense of my body, possessive.

19
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:41,807
I will say something like, you know, I have a headache, but I am ill.

20
00:03:42,508 --> 00:03:47,193
So sometimes we have a body and sometimes we are the body.

