90
00:14:34,712 --> 00:14:40,341
Whatever harm I have done to you in thought, word or deed.

91
00:14:45,769 --> 00:14:49,495
By way of greed, hatred and delusion.

92
00:14:54,823 --> 00:14:59,150
Intentionally, unintentionally, habitually.

93
00:15:04,801 --> 00:15:30,217
I'm sorry for it and I determined from this day on to treat you with due care and respect so now having corrected in some way our relationship to the body

